Author: the_real_blobfish
Text: Something similar happened to me today too! I work at a bakery and I always get closing shifts, which means I have to throw out all the unsold stock from the day (I know it’s hella wasteful it sucks). And I *always* end up binging. Tearing off parts of bread loaves, taking bites out of croissants, stuffing scones in my mouth... BUT today I chewed some gum as I was throwing stuff out and I didn’t binge! There were a couple of points where I wanted to so so bad but *i didn’t*!
